- content_for :title,  "Auto Loans for International Students | Finance Your Vehicle as an International Student"
- content_for :description,"Search for auto loan options available for international students studying in the US to help finance a new or used car."

.container-fluid
  #home-section-1.auto-loans-header.home-section
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %h1{style: 'text-align:center'}
          %br
          Need a car? Finance your vehicle intelligently.      
        #header-button{ style: 'text-align: center'}
          %a{href: new_user_registration_path + "?application_type=auto_loan", class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg'}
            Click Here to Find
            %br.mobile-break
            Your Auto Loan Options
  #home-section-2.home-section{ style: 'background-color:#f5f5f5'}
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-10.offset-1
        %h3 AUTO LOANS
        %p Nomad Credit connects international students attending university in the U.S. with potential lenders based on the search profile they submit on our platform. Just because you haven’t had the chance to build credit yet, doesn’t mean that you shouldn’t own your own car. An auto loan can help you to start building credit today. Nomad Credit can help you find the best solution for your financial situation. Once you see your options, Nomad Credit will be there to help you through the process and answer any questions that you may have.


  #home-section-3.home-section#featured-section{ style: 'background-color:white'}
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-10.offset-1
        %h3 FEATURED LENDER OF THE MONTH
        .row
          .col-md-12{style: 'text-align:center'}
            %a{ href: "https://info.lendbuzz.com/nomad-credit-featured-auto-loan-page/ ", onclick: "gaOutboundLink('partner-Lendbuzz','https://info.lendbuzz.com/nomad-credit-featured-auto-loan-page/ '); return false;"}
              = image_tag 'lendbuzz3.png', height: '120', style: 'margin-top:10px'
        .row
          .col-md-12
            %p{ style: 'text-align:center'} Lendbuzz offers car loans and refinancing options to internationals living in the US with little to no credit history. Our customers include international students, young professionals, expats or anyone with a thin US credit file. Lendbuzz uses an online platform and data-intensive scoring technology in order to make it easier for our customers to access and manage their loans. By considering aspects that traditional lenders do not, such as background information and earning potential, we can offer loans at very attractive terms to internationals.


